{
  "id": "RAW_73cbb94c",
  "title": "刚刚， AI 视频王者大更新！硬刚 Sora，威尔史密斯吃面更香了",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1641061?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2025-10-16 09:27:09",
  "author": "张子豪",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>OpenAI 前不久刚推出了 Sora 2 视频生成模型，势头相当凶猛，紧随其后，今天 Google 的 Veo 3.1 也迎来了一次重大升级。</p>\n  <p>具体来看，Google 这次的升级包括两个层面。</p>\n  <p>一是<strong>功能层面的完善</strong>。视频编辑功能得到了强化，用户现在可以对片段进行更细致的调整，对最终画面有了更精准的掌控。</p>\n  <p id=\"atqPmbe\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03e91190d8.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641062 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03e91190d8.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03e91190d8.png!720 1090w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03e91190d8-360x198.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03e91190d8-768x421.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03e91190d8-1024x562.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1090px) 100vw, 1090px\"></a></p>\n  <p>更重要的是，Google 首次给「素材转视频（Ingredients to Video）」「帧转视频（Frames to Video）」和「延展（Extend）」这些功能配上了音频，让音频成为创作流程的一部分。</p>\n  <p>二是模型层面的进步。</p>\n  <p>今天发布的 Veo 3.1 在提示词理解和视听质量两个关键指标上都有了明显提升，从图像到视频的转化因此更加自然流畅。</p>\n  <p>相关阅读 <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/MYytERqKqzV-pCQ7Rj9jmw\">🔗AI 视频新王全球爆火，威尔·斯密斯终于可以好好吃面（附大量实测演示）</a></p>\n  <p id=\"WxZTtCK\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ea540e1a.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641063 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ea540e1a.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ea540e1a.png!720 1094w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ea540e1a-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ea540e1a-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ea540e1a-1024x573.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1094px) 100vw, 1094px\"></a></p>\n  <p>众所周知，Veo 3 原本就有不少编辑能力在身——通过参考图像指导角色生成、用首尾两帧填充中间内容、基于视频末尾继续延展等操作都可以做。</p>\n  <p>Veo 3.1 的做法是在这些既有功能上全部加入音频支持，让用户能够打造更加完整的场景。这些功能目前还处于实验阶段，Google 表示会根据用户反馈继续优化迭代。</p>\n  <p id=\"rrMgjQu\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ec26f538.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641064 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ec26f538.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ec26f538.png!720 1088w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ec26f538-360x200.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ec26f538-768x426.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ec26f538-1024x568.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1088px) 100vw, 1088px\"></a></p>\n  <p>现在用户可以这样使用这些功能：</p>\n  <p>1、用多张参考图像定义角色、物体和风格，「素材转视频」功能就会根据这些素材生成最终场景。</p>\n  <p id=\"UypjLIo\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ef32ac81.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641065 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ef32ac81.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ef32ac81.png!720 1084w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ef32ac81-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ef32ac81-768x428.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03ef32ac81-1024x571.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px\"></a></p>\n  <p>2、或者提供起始和结束画面，让「帧转视频」功能在中间生成无缝过渡，这对需要艺术性转场的项目特别有用。</p>\n  <p id=\"qsULzNd\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f065e93a.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641066 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f065e93a.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f065e93a.png!720 1088w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f065e93a-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f065e93a-768x433.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f065e93a-1024x578.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1088px) 100vw, 1088px\"></a></p>\n  <p>3、如果要生成更长的视频，「延展」功能可以生成超过一分钟的内容，基于前一段继续生成，保持故事的连贯性。</p>\n  <p id=\"QWyUkDX\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f17b8e99.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641067 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f17b8e99.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f17b8e99.png!720 1084w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f17b8e99-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f17b8e99-768x429.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f17b8e99-1024x572.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px\"></a></p>\n  <p>值得一提的是，Veo 3 的文本转视频此前只支持 720p 横屏输出，但随着竖屏视频成为互联网内容的主流格式，Veo 3.1 现在也可同时生成横屏和竖屏的 16:9 视频，更符合当前的内容消费习惯。\n   <br>\n   创意的打磨往往需要反复迭代。</p>\n  <p>自 Flow 于今年 5 月推出以来，用户已经在该应用中创作了超过 2.75 亿个视频。吸取用户的反馈之后，Flow 中新增的两个编辑功能就是为此而生——</p>\n  <p>「插入新元素」让用户可以随时添加内容，Flow 会自动处理阴影和光线，使新增部分自然融入原有画面；</p>\n  <p>「移除对象」功能（即将上线）则可以删除不需要的元素，Flow 自动重建背景保持一致性。这两个工具的组合能够让视频的编辑过程变得更加灵活。</p>\n  <p id=\"kbbBugK\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f37d3e02.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641068 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f37d3e02.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f37d3e02.png!720 1090w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f37d3e02-360x199.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f37d3e02-768x426.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f37d3e02-1024x567.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1090px) 100vw, 1090px\"></a></p>\n  <p>目前 Veo 3.1 模型已经上线，开发者可以通过 Gemini API 使用，企业用户可在 Vertex AI 中访问，普通用户也可以在 Gemini 应用内体验。新功能也同步在 Gemini API 和 Vertex AI 中开放。</p>\n  <p id=\"MIJfDSE\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f51a1dff.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641069 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f51a1dff.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f51a1dff.png!720 1112w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f51a1dff-360x217.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f51a1dff-768x463.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f51a1dff-1024x617.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1112px) 100vw, 1112px\"></a></p>\n  <p>我们体验生成了 3 个 Veo 最实用的应用场景。</p>\n  <p>前些时间爆火的第一视角穿越、ASMR 切水果，金属、兔子蹦床的夜视监控等视频，都是使用 Veo 3 生成的。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f685e936.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641070 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f685e936.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f685e936.png!720 1084w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f685e936-360x199.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f685e936-768x425.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f685e936-1024x567.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px\"></a></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲由 Veo 3 生成，提示词：50mm camera, close-up angle of a lemon made out of yellow-tinted glass being sliced horizontally on a wooden cutting board. The inside of the fruit is glass as well with a little bit of melting glitter. The entire scene is soft lit from the above.</p>\n  </div>\n  <p id=\"fsaVBuv\">比如这个生成玻璃柠檬的例子。提示词要求「用黄色玻璃制成的柠檬被水平切开，内部也是玻璃材质，里面有融化的闪粉，顶部柔和照亮」。</p>\n  <p>Veo 3 的输出是可用的，但 Veo 3.1 对「融化闪粉」的细节刻画更精准。</p>\n  <p id=\"lHYhVVQ\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f9050850.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641071 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f9050850.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f9050850.png!720 1078w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f9050850-360x200.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f9050850-768x427.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03f9050850-1024x570.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1078px) 100vw, 1078px\"></a></p>\n  <p>电商场景下，我们直接让他生成一段产品的广告。要知道，一般的 TVC（电视商业广告）也就是在 15s/30s 的时间左右来传递品牌信息。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fa5aefb7.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641072 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fa5aefb7.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fa5aefb7.png!720 1084w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fa5aefb7-360x199.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fa5aefb7-768x424.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fa5aefb7-1024x565.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px\"></a></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲由 Sora 2 生成，提示词：根据以下商品信息，生成一段电商广告视频，包含实拍感的产品展示、3D旋转细节、使用场景对比，以及配套字幕。智能手表 X2，续航7天，¥1299 智能手表，50米防水，健康监测（心电、睡眠）</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>Sora 2 贴心地用中文语音解说了商品信息，体现了更好的理解。但 Veo 3.1 这边只是简单地配了音乐，不如 Sora 2 周到，但从画面质量来看，Veo 3.1 的视觉呈现更高级、更有商业感。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fc8df443.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641073 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fc8df443.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fc8df443.png!720 1078w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fc8df443-360x200.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fc8df443-768x426.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fc8df443-1024x568.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1078px) 100vw, 1078px\"></a></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲由 Veo 3.1 生成</p>\n  </div>\n  <p id=\"afcTnit\">我们也试了动漫生成，这次 Veo 3.1 的表现就比较一般了。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fe94e558.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641074 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fe94e558.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fe94e558.png!720 1082w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fe94e558-360x200.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fe94e558-768x426.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f03fe94e558-1024x568.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1082px) 100vw, 1082px\"></a></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲由 Sora 2 生成，提示词：以吉卜力工作室动画风格，一个男孩和他的狗跑上一座长满青草的风景秀丽的山丘，背景远处可以看到一个村庄，天空中飘着美丽的云朵</p>\n  </div>\n  <p id=\"fiBZtZA\">显然 Veo 3.1 在这块的训练数据还不够丰富，距离吉卜力工作室那种精致的动画风格还是有不少差距。莫名消失的狗，都是 AI 穿帮的典型特征。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f0400a7fcdd.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641075 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f0400a7fcdd.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f0400a7fcdd.png!720 1082w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f0400a7fcdd-360x198.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f0400a7fcdd-768x423.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f0400a7fcdd-1024x564.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1082px) 100vw, 1082px\"></a></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲由 Veo 3.1 生成</p>\n  </div>\n  <p id=\"ULVoYoI\">X 网友 @aisearchio 分享的威尔·史密斯吃面测试 Demo 整体质感往上抬了一个档次，动作流畅度、光影细节都明显改善，表情丰富但也没有崩掉。</p>\n  <p id=\"gpMyrQs\"><a href=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f04028e21e2.png!720\" rel=\"lightbox[1641061]\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1641076 \" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f04028e21e2.png!720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f04028e21e2.png!720 1086w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f04028e21e2-360x200.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f04028e21e2-768x427.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_68f04028e21e2-1024x570.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1086px) 100vw, 1086px\"></a></p>\n  <p>综合来看，Veo 3.1 在照片级、商业级的内容生成上已经足够可用，细节理解能力也有明显进步。但在特定风格的精准还原上——比如动漫、插画这类需要高度风格约束的领域，还是有相当的优化空间。\n   <br>\n   尽管如此，从 Veo 3 到 Veo 3.1，从 Sora 到 Sora 2，视频生成模型的迭代速度已经超过了大多数人的想象。</p>\n  <p>伴随着这类 AI 视频生成工具会从专业工具逐渐演变为大众应用，届时，你的朋友圈、短视频平台、甚至新闻源中，每一条内容都有可能是 AI 生成的。</p>\n  <p>这也意味未来你看到的每一条内容，都需要多一步确认——这来自真实拍摄，还是 AI 生成。</p>\n  <p>作者：莫崇宇</p>\n  <p>文章内视频链接：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/qBOkoWaGF5k7oPCR_H5aqA\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/qBOkoWaGF5k7oPCR_H5aqA</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google Veo 3.1 迎来重大更新，强化视频编辑并首次支持音频，提升提示词理解和视听质量，与 Sora 2 在多场景下展开对比。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google Veo 3.1 迎来重大更新，强化视频编辑并首次支持音频，提升提示词理解和视听质量，与 Sora 2 在多场景下展开对比。",
